<title>ạlly yjylk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạlly yjylk rby ḥạlạaⁿ rạḥ ylạqyk ylqy̱ mḥbh wnʿmh wkẖyr mn mlʾ ạydyk
 1-ysẖbʿ byk ytldẖdẖ tftḥ lh ạ̉ḥḍạnk ynsy̱ ạlwqt mʿạk yạrby mạ ạ̉ḥly̱ klạmk
 tksẖf fkrk rby wtʿln dẖạtk lyh dh ạlly yjylk
 2-tftḥ dẖhnh wyʿrf ạ̹zạy qlbk ḥbh mt wkạnt klfẗ wṣrt kẖṭyẗ lạ̉jlh
 kl gẖnạk ybqy̱ lh wtmlạ ạlgẖrbh ʿlyh lmạ yjylk
 3-ymsk byk ytʿlq ʿạrfk htnjyh mhmạ ạn kạn ạlḍyq wạtẖq fy gẖlạwth ʿlyk
 wạlmwạʿyd ạn ṭạlt lạzm tyjy ạ̉kyd bs yjylk</lyrics>
